WHAT INFORMATION DO WE COLLECT?
Personal information you disclose to us
We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide when you register, use features of the application, or contact us.

Personal Information may include:

Names

Phone numbers

Email addresses

Usernames

Sensitive Information

When necessary and with your consent, we may process:

Government-issued identifiers (if required by law)

Social Media Login Data

If you choose to register using a social media account (such as Facebook or X), we may receive certain profile information from that provider.

Application Data

If you use the Raya application, we may request access to:

Geolocation information

Camera and storage

Push notifications

This data is used only to operate and improve the application.

HOW DO WE PROCESS YOUR INFORMATION?
We process your information to:

Create and manage user accounts

Provide application features

Improve performance and security

Prevent fraud and comply with legal requirements

WHEN AND WITH WHOM DO WE SHARE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?
We may share information only in limited situations, such as:

Business transfers (merger, sale, or acquisition)

HOW DO WE HANDLE YOUR SOCIAL LOGINS?
If you log in using social media, we receive information allowed by that platform and use it only for account creation and login purposes.

HOW LONG DO WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION?
We retain personal information only as long as necessary while you have an active account or as required by law.

HOW DO WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION SAFE?
We use reasonable technical and organizational security measures, but no system is 100% secure.

DO WE COLLECT INFORMATION FROM MINORS?
We do not knowingly collect data from children under 18 years of age.

WHAT ARE YOUR PRIVACY RIGHTS?
You may:

Access or update your account information

Request deletion of your data

Withdraw consent at any time

CONTROLS FOR DO-NOT-TRACK FEATURES
We currently do not respond to Do-Not-Track browser signals.

DO WE MAKE UPDATES TO THIS NOTICE?
Yes. We may update this notice to stay compliant with applicable laws.

HOW CAN YOU CONTACT US ABOUT THIS NOTICE?
Email: ahmed.ethofy.is2025@gmail.com

HOW CAN YOU REVIEW, UPDATE, OR DELETE YOUR DATA?
You may contact us to request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data.
